name: Number_digitsTest
description: Unit tests for the Number class's digits method.

test_cases.name: testDigitsWithPositiveCount
test_cases.description: Tests the digits method with a positive count, ensuring the result length matches the count and all characters are digits.

test_cases.name: testDigitsWithZeroCount
test_cases.description: Tests the digits method with a zero count, ensuring the result length is zero.

test_cases.name: testDigitsWithNegativeCount
test_cases.description: Tests the digits method with a negative count, ensuring the result length is zero after applying Math.max.

test_cases.name: testDigitsWithSingleDigit
test_cases.description: Tests the digits method with a single digit count, ensuring the result length is one and the character is a digit.
